_sText:
A full texture map, its great for everyone. there's a more wide open space for people who enjoy snipers, the maze for close combat, and the building for a mix as well as a ladder up to the roof of the building so you can sniper unexpected maze victims. Enjoy!

 *Note* I made this map more for fun gameplay than for looks just for the record, I'm hoping since there's 3 alternate routes gameplay won't get repetetive
